{"title":"Set Your Transmission Free w/ New WTC Chainrings for Race Face & SRAM 3-Bolt","link":"https://bikerumor.com/sram-transmission-wtc-chainrings-race-face-cinch-sram-3-bolt/","date":1692802773000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2.jpeg\" alt=\"WTC Race Face Direct Mount transmission chainring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2.jpeg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_2-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Want the new SRAM Transmission, but don’t want to buy a new crankset? It was only a matter of time before brands started offering different T-Type compatible chainrings, and not surprisingly, Wolf Tooth Components has stepped up to the plate. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Race Face Cinch</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1.jpeg\"><img width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1.jpeg\" alt=\"WTC Race Face Direct Mount transmission chainring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1.jpeg 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Wolf-Tooth_Direct-Mount-for-RFC_1-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For their Race Face models, WTC took their existing Cinch direct mount rings and updated them for T-Type. That means designing them for the new 55mm chainline, and adding their Drop-Stop B tooth profile that is optimized for T-Type chains. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Race Face Cinch T-Type rings will be offered in 32, 34, and 36t round rings, and 32, and 34t oval rings.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>SRAM 3-Bolt Direct Mount</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"WTC SRAM 3-bolt direct mount transmission chainring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_30T_MRKT-0029-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"WTC SRAM 3-bolt direct mount transmission chainring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/WT23_SRAM-3-Bolt-Direct-Mount-Chainring_0mm_Oval_32T_MRKT-0055-Large.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Since all of the SRAM Transmission chainrings use the newer 8-bolt mounting pattern, WTC is also making 3-bolt chainrings for SRAM’s own cranksets. That, or any other crank that uses the older 3-bolt direct mount pattern. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>These rings will be offered in 30, 32, 34, and 36t round, and 30, 32, and 34t oval options. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And if you have any questions about what exact chainring you need to install a new SRAM drivetrain on your bike, WTC put together <a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/pages/how-to-find-the-correct-chainring-for-your-mountain-bike-with-sram-transmission\" target=\"_blank\">this handy guide</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.wolftoothcomponents.com/collections/mountain\" target=\"_blank\">wolftoothcomponents.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/sram-transmission-wtc-chainrings-race-face-cinch-sram-3-bolt/\">Set Your Transmission Free w/ New WTC Chainrings for Race Face &amp; SRAM 3-Bolt</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"2f1598915f64d182456f89862b74e4d3c1634626ed69130d01fc50b418cd6f36","category":"Cycling"}